---
title: Easy Sichuan Garlic Beef Rump Tacos with Slaw & Parsley
description: Sichuan and garlic have come together in a deal to create tacos that no one can refuse. They are giving beef rump a new lease on life and the sesame seeds help to seal the deal. If you read the fine print, it’s guaranteed that these tacos will have everyone at your table feeling full and satisfied.
